Online job platform, Jobberman has launched an employer-focused initiative, “Jobberman Starter Promo”, aimed at contributing to employment growth and providing an enabling environment for employers looking to give young talents a head start.  Boboye said the Jobberman Starter promo initiative and its partnership with the Mastercard Foundation advance its commitment to solving talent issues in the country and contributing to reducing Nigeria’s unemployment rate.
  
Jobberman said it aims to continue being Nigeria’s most user-centric and transparent career platform while calling on candidates interested in this initiative to visit www.jobberman.com/employer/entrylevel and get started.